    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是一个道德抉择场景。那罗得本人需要出现在图中吗？第七章也提到了他的行为。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Lot"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，罗得的行为形成对比。他把自己的女儿献给暴徒，却存活且兴旺。这和他的妻子形成鲜明对照。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Lot",
        "Moral Evaluation",
        "Offers Daughters to Rapists",
        "Survives and Prospers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建主干结构。左侧放罗得妻子，她连接到疏散选择节点；下方另起一支放罗得，连到道德评估节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "E",
        "F"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "罗得妻子的两个分支我命名为「向前看」和「回头看」，分别导向存活和化为盐柱。这样表达准确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Look Forward",
        "Look Back",
        "Survives",
        "Executed as Salt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "准确。化为盐柱是文本中的直接描述，保留「Executed as Salt」这个表述。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "罗得的分支需要更完整：他献出女儿后，箭头要指向「存活且兴旺」。这个结局和他的妻子形成讽刺对比。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "G",
        "H"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在两条故事线都完整了。我注意到罗得的行为在道德上很有争议，需要视觉区分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "H"
